[{"id":"VR852963","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">For which of the following two-object systems, if any, is the total momentum constant?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR852963_rubric","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A pendulum is attached to a frame that is on wheels. The frame is free to move back and forth on a horizontal surface as the pendulum oscillates. The figures show the sphere and the frame at three different times.</p>\n\n<ul class=\"unordered_list style:1\">\n\t<li class=\"list_item\">\n\t<p class=\"list_paragraph\">Figure <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"1\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> shows when the pendulum is at its maximum leftward displacement.</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li class=\"list_item\">\n\t<p class=\"list_paragraph\">Figure <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"2\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> shows when the pendulum is instantaneously at its equilibrium position.</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li class=\"list_item\">\n\t<p class=\"list_paragraph\">Figure <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"3\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>3</mn></math></span></span> shows when the pendulum is at its maximum rightward displacement.</p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"standalone_image\">\n\n<img alt=\"Three figures are shown. Each figure shows a pendulum attached to the top edge of a frame that is on wheels. In Figure 1, the pendulum slants downward and to the left from where it is attached to the frame. In Figure 2, the pendulum is shown moving from left to right and extends vertically downward from where it is attached to the frame. The frame moves from right to left. In figure 3, the pendulum slants downward and to the right from where it is attached to the frame.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR852963.g01.svg\"></div>"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The frame-sphere system</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The frame-Earth system</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The sphere-Earth system</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">None of these two-object systems have a constant momentum.</p>"],"answer":3}]